data.description: Welcome to this charming three-bedroom, one-bathroom home nestled within the city limits of Vine Grove. Built in 1939, this historic gem boasts timeless character offering a cozy haven for comfortable living.  Featuring newer appliances, stove and refrigerator.  Water heater was replaced 1 year ago.  Furnace is 2 years old and a new roof last year.  Outside, the property boasts a large, detached garage, providing secure parking and additional storage space.  The backyard offers a tranquil retreat, perfect for entertaining or unwinding after a long day. Located within city limits, this home offers easy access to schools, parks, and entertainment options.  Don’t miss out on the opportunity to make this residence your own, schedule a showing today!
